LEADERSHIP : The Police Command in Bayelsa has said that its personnel are working round the clock to ensure that the kidnapped mother of Samson Siasia, Nigeria’s former Super Eagles footballer is rescued from her captors. SP Asinim Butswat, the spokesperson of the command made this known in a text message with Newsmen in Yenagoa on Sunday. […] The post We Are Working Round The Clock To Ensure Release Of Siasia Mother’s— Police appeared first on Leadership Newspaper and NNN. Source: Leadership News